Steps i have done in the github actions:
==========================================
1. I have taken a simple springboot LOGIN page application
2. Which is simple java and maven project
3. In github actions i build the project and stored the artifact in target
4. After building the Jar file 
5. Written a Dockerfile for creating docker image with that Dockerfile created image are stored in my Dockerhub repo
6. The Dockerhub credentails i mentioned as secret 
7. Once the docker image is build it will stored in my dockerhub repo.
8. After that i written a Deployment in kubernetes cluster with service
Deployment:
============
In Deployment i written with two replica's and a service type Loadbalancer i mentioned so that i can access the application on browser.
for sample deployment i didn't take any PV,PVC and Healthchecks
